# Environment Variables Template
# Copy this file to your workspace and fill in the values
# DO NOT commit secrets to version control

# ===========================================
# Supermemory API Key
# ===========================================
# Get your API key from: https://app.supermemory.ai/?view=integrations
# SUPERMEMORY_API_KEY=sm_your_api_key_here

# ===========================================
# OpenCode Plugin API Keys
# ===========================================
# Add API keys for plugins as needed
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...
# OPENROUTER_API_KEY=sk-or-...

# ===========================================
# Custom MCP Server Variables
# ===========================================
# SEARXNG_URL=http://100.110.14.68:8080/
# Add custom MCP server env vars here

# ===========================================
# Usage Notes
# ===========================================
# 1. Copy this file to your workspace as .env (or .env.local)
# 2. Fill in your API keys and secrets
# 3. Add .env to .gitignore if it contains secrets
# 4. Source the file in your shell if needed: source .env